match.name: November SPARC Match
match.about:
Match will consist of 7 stages. Par times for stages will be 90 seconds. Expect a total of 50-60 impacts required for the match. The DMR/SPR division is now called the open division. This match will count toward season standing. The match will be scored on a time plus scoring basis.

Range will go hot for zero at 8 am until 8:30 am. From 8:30 am - 9:00 am will be mandatory shooter safety and stage brief. This match is a squad RO'd and squad scored match. Please be prepared to help score and spot for your squad.

The coordinates of the match location are below:

(39.9035594, -111.8352742)
